@memory-mcp-server
Feature: Memory MCP Server
  As a Claude Desktop user replacing the Graphiti MCP
  I want memory_search, memory_write_payload and memory_supersede tools and a project-listing resource exposed over stdio
  So that a Desktop session can read and write typed fleet-memory through the one deterministic write path, with no crash when the store is down

  Background:
    Given the memory MCP server is running over stdio transport
    And the fleet-memory store is reachable and populated with typed payloads for project "guardkit"
    And the embedding service is available

